{"title":"Cycles Manivelle Frame Bags","link":"https://theradavist.com/cycles-manivelle-frame-bags","date":1772636762000,"content":"<p><em>France’s <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/cycles-manivelle\" target=\"_blank\">Cycles Manivelle</a>, makers of that stunning touring bike <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2025-bespoked-dresden-picks-04#:~:text=Cycles%20Manivelle%20Effigear%20Tourer\" target=\"_blank\">from the 2025 Bespoked Dresden show</a>, just announced <a href=\"https://cyclesmanivelle.com/en/-boutique/bags/framebag/\" target=\"_blank\">its line of frame bags</a>…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-2.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-2.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-4.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-4.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-4.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-4.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Manivelle hesitated a little before deciding to add a frame bag to its range of bags. While it’s a simple product, there are already quite many options on the market. And then the small bag maker and framebuilder operation realized that it could make its offerings more affordable, thanks to a series production, made in France, from upcycled materials, with waterproof laminated textiles in fun colors.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-9.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-9.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-9.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-9.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-7.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-7.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-7.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-7.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Manivelle frame bags are laced around the frame to distribute tension evenly around the bag, ensuring easy handling. The contour of the bag is structured with a foam, just the right amount. The seam of the zip is waterproofed with a thermal tape, and the contour is finished off with a cordura strip, so that the bag can withstand as much rain as possible. The bag stays simple, has a zipper on each side for access to the main compartment and a flat pocket, and a cable  on the front.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-20.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-20.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-20.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-20.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-17.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-17.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-17.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-17.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-14.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-14.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-14.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Cycles-Manivelle-Frame-Bags-14.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The Manivelle frame bag is available in three sizes, depending on the size of your frame and/or your needs:</p>\n<p>S / 300x100mm, ~100gr<br />\nM / (380x120mm, ~130gr<br />\nL / 490x160mm, ~160gr</p>\n<p>The patterns are laser-cut, to reduce manufacturing time and offer the bag at the best possible price. Each bag is then hand-sewn in our workshop. We regularly produce small batches, in between the custom-made productions of our textile workshop. Manivelle will also make custom bags, so inquire if you’d like one.</p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://cyclesmanivelle.com/en/-boutique/bags/framebag/\" target=\"_blank\">Manivelle</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/cycles-manivelle-frame-bags\">Cycles Manivelle Frame Bags</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://cms.theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"e40bdb7988132898e1438afe30a93b243e4e91a39d5befea991eed1f08c6845d","category":"Cycling"}